161
00:09:02,710 --> 00:09:04,350
Before heading abroad,

162
00:09:04,730 --> 00:09:06,210
you'll all go to the Navy Museum.

163
00:09:06,650 --> 00:09:08,490
Take a look at our ancestors' legacy.

164
00:09:08,810 --> 00:09:11,530
Feel what it means to go from nothing,

165
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,650
to weak, to strong.

166
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,730
