Xin, come on. Please.

566
00:30:54,650 --> 00:30:55,190
Hi.

567
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:59,410
Do you know
where the outdoor supplies store is?

568
00:30:59,530 --> 00:31:01,150
Turn right,

569
00:31:01,150 --> 00:31:03,770
go past the street,
and you'll arrive at your destination.

570
00:31:03,770 --> 00:31:04,760
Okay. Thank you!

571
00:31:04,850 --> 00:31:06,048
- Let's go!
- Are you serious?

572
00:31:06,048 --> 00:31:07,580
Hey, it's better

573
00:31:07,580 --> 00:31:08,982
if you don't stay there overnight.

574
00:31:20,590 --> 00:31:21,410
Ding.

575
00:31:25,490 --> 00:31:26,180
Mr. Han.

576
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:28,610
I saw on Miss Tang's Moments

577
00:31:28,610 --> 00:31:29,890
that she's currently overseas.

578
00:31:29,970 --> 00:31:30,980
Find out

579
00:31:31,090 --> 00:31:32,170
when she left,

580
00:31:32,210 --> 00:31:33,115
and where she went.

581
00:31:33,137 --> 00:31:33,826
Okay.

582
00:31:44,150 --> 00:31:45,970
Slow down, Yangyang!

583
00:31:46,410 --> 00:31:49,290
Xin, look at all these trees!

584
00:31:53,410 --> 00:31:55,330
I'll find that fruit!

585
00:31:57,970 --> 00:31:59,730
Where are you hiding?

586
00:32:03,970 --> 00:32:05,850
Wait up! Be careful.

587
00:32:08,210 --> 00:32:09,050
Hello,

588
00:32:09,050 --> 00:32:11,370
everybody! Hi!

589
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:13,380
Today,

590
00:32:13,380 --> 00:32:14,480
I'm taking everyone

591
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:16,890
on a spontaneous,

592
00:32:16,890 --> 00:32:18,090
unplugged adventure.

593
00:32:19,850 --> 00:32:21,280
Let me show you real quick.

594
00:32:21,970 --> 00:32:23,490
- This...
- Don't film me.

595
00:32:23,890 --> 00:32:26,810
This is one of An's most famous

596
00:32:26,810 --> 00:32:28,000
natural forests.

597
00:32:55,730 --> 00:32:57,930
(Hello. I'm a friend of Miss Tang's.)

598
00:32:57,982 --> 00:32:59,379
(Miss Tang is away on assignment)

599
00:32:59,380 --> 00:33:00,570
(and won't be back anytime soon.)

600
00:33:00,570 --> 00:33:01,669
(She asked me to contact you)

601
00:33:01,670 --> 00:33:03,580
(and request that you continue
providing leads to me.)

602
00:33:03,580 --> 00:33:04,937
(I'll investigate on her behalf.)

603
00:33:13,610 --> 00:33:16,570
(May I ask what your profession is?)

604
00:33:19,540 --> 00:33:21,610
(I run a business.
I've got an extensive network.)

605
00:33:21,830 --> 00:33:23,790
(I can help Miss Tang in a lot of ways.)

606
00:33:23,930 --> 00:33:25,170
(I've helped her before too.)

607
00:33:30,740 --> 00:33:33,180
(Did Miss Tang give you
this email address?)

608
00:33:49,320 --> 00:33:51,810
(Yes. Can you send me the lead now?)

609
00:33:58,570 --> 00:33:59,250
(Miss Tang,)

610
00:33:59,293 --> 00:34:00,200
(someone contacted us)

611
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:02,050
(through the email we used before,)

612
00:34:02,093 --> 00:34:03,290
(claiming to be your friend)

613
00:34:03,550 --> 00:34:05,340
(and asking for the lead.)

614
00:34:06,130 --> 00:34:07,170
(Is that true?)

615
00:34:13,050 --> 00:34:14,050
Lan Yangyang,

616
00:34:15,200 --> 00:34:16,670
what does that fruit

617
00:34:16,930 --> 00:34:18,240
look like?

618
00:34:21,890 --> 00:34:23,330
I sent you a photo of it, didn't I?

619
00:34:24,810 --> 00:34:25,530
Did you?

620
00:34:25,530 --> 00:34:26,110
I did.

621
00:34:27,170 --> 00:34:27,820
Let me see...

622
00:34:33,690 --> 00:34:34,330
Is this it?

623
00:34:34,330 --> 00:34:35,400
Is this the fruit?

624
00:34:39,050 --> 00:34:39,640
No.

625
00:34:42,210 --> 00:34:43,930
This is it!

626
00:34:47,050 --> 00:34:47,930
Look, Xin!

627
00:34:50,990 --> 00:34:52,030
We won't find anything

628
00:34:52,030 --> 00:34:53,770
with your questionable eyesight.

629
00:34:53,770 --> 00:34:55,850
The shape clearly doesn't match.

630
00:34:59,330 --> 00:35:01,240
It's fine. We just started.

631
00:35:01,240 --> 00:35:02,550
We'll keep going. Come on!

632
00:35:03,330 --> 00:35:03,850
Come on!

633
00:35:05,250 --> 00:35:06,570
Everyone,

634
00:35:07,930 --> 00:35:08,850
we've hit

635
00:35:08,850 --> 00:35:11,210
a slight obstacle.

636
00:35:11,210 --> 00:35:12,360
We haven't found it yet.

637
00:35:13,530 --> 00:35:14,650
But if we do,

638
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:17,690
I'll show you

639
00:35:17,690 --> 00:35:18,930
right away

640
00:35:19,330 --> 00:35:21,230
what it looks like.

641
00:35:21,230 --> 00:35:21,850
Okay?

642
00:35:21,850 --> 00:35:23,290
Stay tuned!

643
00:35:29,930 --> 00:35:31,510
Xin, it's lagging.

644
00:35:31,510 --> 00:35:32,580
No signal?

645
00:35:34,810 --> 00:35:35,710
I'll check my phone.

646
00:35:40,850 --> 00:35:41,650
Yangyang,

647
00:35:42,330 --> 00:35:43,400
we should turn back.

648
00:35:43,560 --> 00:35:44,830
Looks like we're out of range.

649
00:35:44,982 --> 00:35:46,137
Let's not go any deeper.

650
00:35:47,080 --> 00:35:48,030
No way.

651
00:35:48,030 --> 00:35:49,820
What if there's a signal further in?

652
00:35:49,826 --> 00:35:52,093
How are we going to find it
if we don't go further?

653
00:35:52,170 --> 00:35:53,330
Come on!

654
00:35:53,330 --> 00:35:54,550
I'm sure it'll be fine in there.

655
00:35:57,310 --> 00:35:59,170
Do we have to find that fruit?

656
00:36:00,170 --> 00:36:01,010
Yes!

657
00:36:24,850 --> 00:36:25,690
Do this

658
00:36:27,090 --> 00:36:28,090
and then this...

659
00:36:31,090 --> 00:36:31,810
Done.

660
00:36:38,210 --> 00:36:39,050
Yangyang!

661
00:36:39,950 --> 00:36:40,930
Wait for me!

662
00:36:46,650 --> 00:36:50,140
This mission is about
a submerged search.

663
00:36:50,339 --> 00:36:53,829
We've installed field mission boxes

664
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:56,370
all over the bottom of the ocean.

665
00:36:57,470 --> 00:36:59,490
You must find them all

666
00:36:59,490 --> 00:37:02,130
according to the time and route.

667
00:37:03,050 --> 00:37:04,890
The shortest time wins.

668
00:37:05,782 --> 00:37:07,930
You cannot switch people.

669
00:37:07,930 --> 00:37:10,450
If you have a risky situation,

670
00:37:10,540 --> 00:37:12,330
you call the rescue team.

671
00:37:12,330 --> 00:37:14,320
If you call the rescue team,

672
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,190
you lose.

673
00:37:15,930 --> 00:37:16,490
So,

674
00:37:17,330 --> 00:37:19,090
do you understand me?

675
00:37:19,370 --> 00:37:20,730
Yes, Sir.

676
00:37:20,970 --> 00:37:21,810
Again!

677
00:37:22,030 --> 00:37:23,220
I can't hear you!

678
00:37:23,640 --> 00:37:26,250
Do you understand me?

679
00:37:26,380 --> 00:37:27,550
Yes, Sir!

680
00:37:49,826 --> 00:37:51,320
Wang Chen and I will be the first team.

681
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:53,204
Zong Qing and Yi Nanwang,
you two provide backup.

682
00:37:54,382 --> 00:37:56,337
Wang Chen,
we'll split up once we're underwater.

683
00:37:56,382 --> 00:37:58,570
Three, two, one.

684
00:37:58,570 --> 00:38:00,570
Go, go, go!

685
00:38:24,300 --> 00:38:28,300
(Underwater in An, Wu Si)

686
00:40:52,770 --> 00:40:53,350
Captain Zong.

687
00:40:53,448 --> 00:40:55,315
Captain Wu brought up
a member of An's navy.

688
00:40:55,337 --> 00:40:56,850
There's a problem with his oxygen tank.

689
00:40:56,850 --> 00:40:58,226
I hope Captain Chen's doing okay.

690
00:41:04,420 --> 00:41:07,740
(Underwater in An, Wang Chen)

691
00:42:23,341 --> 00:42:26,821
♪The vast sky and sea,
this deep blue expanse♪

692
00:42:27,511 --> 00:42:30,781
♪So deep, so boundless♪

693
00:42:31,121 --> 00:42:34,291
♪Just like your arms♪

694
00:42:34,781 --> 00:42:37,901
♪Shielding me from the dark clouds♪

695
00:42:38,191 --> 00:42:41,831
♪Always bearing it all in silence♪

696
00:42:41,831 --> 00:42:48,251
♪Even the long, long road gives me peace
when you're there♪

697
00:42:48,751 --> 00:42:53,151
♪Not one to show romance
in front of others♪

698
00:42:53,611 --> 00:42:56,701
♪You speak of dreams
with such calm simplicity♪

699
00:42:57,491 --> 00:43:02,291
♪But I know your heart
holds much deeper hopes♪

700
00:43:04,561 --> 00:43:06,401
♪I truly understand♪

701
00:43:06,891 --> 00:43:11,081
♪You speak of love so slowly♪

702
00:43:11,331 --> 00:43:17,301
♪But your eyes have already
told me everything♪

703
00:43:17,807 --> 00:43:20,497
♪Using up all my fortune♪

704
00:43:20,501 --> 00:43:24,901
♪Just to trade a lifetime with you♪

705
00:43:24,991 --> 00:43:27,211
♪Thank you for awakening♪

706
00:43:27,221 --> 00:43:32,301
♪The courage once hidden in my fear♪

707
00:43:32,441 --> 00:43:35,631
♪Turning every chance into certainty♪

708
00:43:35,961 --> 00:43:39,491
♪Turning every tie into companionship♪

709
00:43:39,571 --> 00:43:44,541
♪Blooming into brilliance
for all the years to come♪

710
00:43:44,541 --> 00:43:48,531
♪No one can tear us apart♪

711
00:43:48,721 --> 00:43:52,071
♪Each time my palm feels warmth again♪

712
00:43:52,331 --> 00:43:57,671
♪The memories return,
and I'm no longer alone♪

713
00:43:58,561 --> 00:44:02,551
♪No matter how far
across time and space♪

714
00:44:02,801 --> 00:44:06,201
♪My longing reaches you in silence♪

715
00:44:06,321 --> 00:44:10,851
♪No need to call out loudly♪

716
00:44:10,851 --> 00:44:13,521
♪No matter how much it takes♪

717
00:44:13,541 --> 00:44:17,951
♪To bring this drifting heart to shore♪

718
00:44:17,951 --> 00:44:21,211
♪Thank you for standing behind me♪

719
00:44:21,231 --> 00:44:25,281
♪Lighting up the darkness and despair♪

720
00:44:25,281 --> 00:44:28,751
♪The bigger the world,
the lonelier it feels♪

721
00:44:28,751 --> 00:44:32,521
♪Only by your side♪

722
00:44:32,531 --> 00:44:39,611
♪Can I truly feel this warmth inside♪
